<Users API Documentation>
This API provides CRUD operations for managing users.

<Get>
Retrieves user information.

GET /users_api.php
  Returns a list of all users.

GET /users_api.php?id={id}
  Returns information for a specific user.

<Post>
Creates a new user.

POST /users_api.php
  Body: { "name": "Ken", "email": "Ken@streetfhighters.com" }
  Creates a new user with the provided name and email.

<Update>
Updates an existing user's information.

PUT /users_api.php?id={id}
  Body: { "name": "Ken", "email": "Ken@streetfhighters.com" }
  Updates the user with the specified id.

<Delete>
Removes a user from the database.

DELETE /users_api.php?id={id}
  Deletes the user with the specified id.